INSERT INTO `wy_posts` VALUES(1305, 1, '2018-06-17 10:45:54', '2018-06-17 10:45:54', '<p class=\"noind\"><i class=\"calibre6\">                                         Fodilat Sheik YAHQUB ABDUL BAAKI MUHAMMAD   </i></p>\r\n<p class=\"noind\"><i class=\"calibre6\">                                                 The First Wazeer Of Yoruba Land              </i></p>\r\n<p class=\"noind\"><i class=\"calibre6\">             </i></p>\r\n                           From now on, historians will begin to write a new history about Yorubas and our forgotten past about Islam will become the present we are to live for as Oluwo, the Emir of Yorubas finally sets the ball rolling by installing the First Waziri of Yorubaland, Sheikh Yahkub Abdul Baaqi Muhammad.\r\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\r\n\r\nThe installation and turbanning took place on March 31, 2018 at Oluwo Palace in Iwo, the city of Islamic scholars, the home to the first Yoruba mosque, the first Shari’ah court in Nigeria and pacesetter for Arabic poetry that had contributed to Islamic development of the nation.\r\n\r\nIt was a remarkable day for the people of Iwo and the entire Yoruba Muslims as the occasion signals the rebirth of Islam for whoever that has passion for Islamic development in the entire region.\r\n\r\nThe event was graced by people from North, East, South and West of Nigeria with keynote addresses from respected Islamic scholars who are known to be good ambassadors of Islam.\r\n\r\nOn the occasion, the founder and national President of Jama’at Ta’awunil Muslimeen, Sheikh Daood Imran Molaasan made it known that what the Emir of Yorubas has done would create and generate within and outside enemies with aim of putting an end to Allah’s complete project of Islamic revival in Yorubaland which is about to take off.\r\n\r\nHe said, the time has come for every conscious Muslims to see Iwo as their Medinah, where Islamic structure has to be laid just the way Medinah was made during the time of the Prophet Muhammad. (s.a.w).\r\n\r\n“Iwo will be named Islamic Emirate” he said, and asked Almighty Allah to protect and give the Emir and Waziri of Yorubaland long life.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"noind\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-1304\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/alwazeer/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/now-214x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"214\" height=\"300\" /></p>', 'History', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1294-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-06-17 10:45:54', '2018-06-17 10:45:54', '', 1294, 'http://localhost:8888/alwazeer/2018/06/17/1294-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
